    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine remains strong and responsive, while the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, ensuring a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The interior shows minor signs of regular use but remains clean and well-kept, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine with only typical wear for its age. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive with confidence.",
      "price": 34000.0,
