    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and reliable performance. This unit offers a sophisticated driving experience, characterized by its robust mechanical integrity and a well-preserved interior. It represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of performance and long-term value. Every aspect of this vehicle has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and roadworthiness. Service documentation is available to confirm its history of diligent upkeep.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect if you're looking for a smooth, worry-free ride that still looks great in the driveway! I've made sure to keep up with everything so it's ready to go the moment you hop in. It's got plenty of life left and is just waiting for its next adventure. Drop me a message if you want to come by, check it out, and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a remarkably well-maintained E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to achieve its 8,400 RPM redline, delivering a linear power band that is increasingly rare. The 6-speed manual transmission provides a mechanical connection to the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring precise torque distribution across the rear axle. This example features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable suspension geometry and has had the critical rod bearing and throttle actuator services performed proactively. While the paint exhibits minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the chassis remains rigid and the subframe mounting points are in excellent structural condition. A visceral performance machine with a documented service history.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sport coupe strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a weekend enthusiast's dream. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous metallic finish, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, while the dashboard and trim are devoid of sun damage or cracks. All electronic systems, from the premium audio to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a comprehensive service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and a responsive engine that delivers power consistently. Recent updates include a fresh set of high-performance tires and a complete brake service. This is a turn-key vehicle, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without the need for immediate repairs or detailing.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a standard of engineering excellence and consistent care. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure optimal mechanical performance and structural integrity. The interior remains in a refined state, reflecting a history of diligent ownership. Offering a superior balance of luxury and dependability, this vehicle represents a significant opportunity for the discerning motorist seeking long-term value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I've absolutely loved driving this beauty, but it's time for someone else to get behind the wheel. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014it's got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking and running great. It's just a fantastic, dependable ride that's ready for your next adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common floor pan fatigue, and the valve clearances were recently shimmed to factory tolerances. The suspension maintains its composure through the corners thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain top-tier. A true enthusiast's specimen optimized for linear power delivery and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
